  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN350">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>tūrnta kiṭaṅkiṟ cōrnta ñāyiṟ</l>
<l>citainta viñcik katuvāy mūtūr</l>
<l>yāṅkā vatuko ṟāṉē tāṅkātu</l>
<l>paṭumaḻai yurumi ṉiraṅku muraciṟ</l>
<l>kaṭumāṉ vēntar kālai vanten</l>
<l>neṭunilai vāyiṟ koṭkuvar mātō</l>
<l>poruntā tamaruva rallar pōruḻan</l>
<l>taṭumuraṇ muṉpiṟ ṟaṉṉaiya rēntiya</l>
<l>vaṭivē leḵkiṟ civanta vuṇkaṭ</l>
<l>ṭoṭipiṟaḻ muṉkai yiḷaiyō</l>
<l>ḷaṇinal lākat tarumpiya cuṇaṅkē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The blunt old town with ramparts that are ruined,</l>
<l>with bastions that are fallen [and] ditches that are filled up,</l>
<l>how will it become? Not enduring,</l>
<l>as in the morning the king with a fast horse comes,</l>
<l>with drums roaring like the thunder during the falling rains,</l>
<l>will they not swing our doors of long standing [open]?</l>
<l>Inconveniently, the won’t keep quiet, bearing with war,</l>
<l>her people with murderous hostile strength.</l>
<l>Beauty spots have budded on the adorned good breast</l>
<l>of the young one with forearms that sport bangles,</l>
  [her] kajal eyes reddened like the tips of the shapely spears they hold up.   
</lg>
    </div>
